$\Lambda$CDM ($\Lambda$ cold dark matter) model, the low-redshift
constraint is in good agreement with Planck $\Lambda$CDM. This paper is
part of a set that analyses the final galaxy clustering data set from
BOSS. The measurements and likelihoods presented here are combined with
