  abstract = {We analyse the anisotropic clustering of the Baryon Oscillation 
Spectroscopic Survey (BOSS) CMASS Data Release 11 (DR11) sample, which
consists of 690 827 galaxies in the redshift range 0.43 $<$ z $<$ 0.7
and has a sky coverage of 8498 deg2. We perform our analysis
